title: Billie Eilish Answers Increasingly Personal Questions | Slow Zoom | Vanity Fair
author: Vanity Fair
description:
Billie Eilish answers increasingly personal questions as the camera closes in on her. There are 4 categories to these questions: identity, fame, family, and work. From the time she has felt the most vulnerable in her career to what she loves about mosh pits, learn more about Billie as the video goes on.
